list.name: Changes
list.comment: Ported over Big Picture Mode from Proot, added Dark Theme, modified all classes related to new dark theme, completely replaced Turnip Driver switching for shorcuts with a new implementation based on proot build, added xinput disabler for shortcuts via intent to update winhandler, added fullscreen stretched toggle for containers and shortcuts, fixed issue with xinput dinput switching in shortcuts settings, added definable frontend shortcut path, added all new settings to settingsfragment, added animations for all menus, many changes and fixes

task.summary: Default task
Cmod test commit
modified xserverdisplayactivity to handle turnip installations for selections that were added via content manager

added backup and restore to settings, updated tarcompressor with new exclusions methods to avoid overwriting shared prefs during restore, added frontend support modified xserverdisplayactivity to accept container_id as an extra, fixed issue with turnip driver appearing in turnip/virgl selection dropdown, added new playtime tracking and play count stats, updated default turnip version, added additional logging and experimental changes to drawable.c, gpu_image. and gpu_image.java
fixed extract graphics driver method in xserverdisplayactivity where I accidently removed the passing of environmental variables XD

many bug fixes with shortcuts and turnip driver switching, fixed renaming shortcuts, added legacy 7.1.2 dinput xinput mode, many more things I can't remember because I couldn't make commits for a week and a half with no github
